snippet.title: Hot Wheels Unleashed™ 2 - Alien Encounters Expansion Pack
snippet.description:
Race through the wreckage of a UFO and explore suspended walkways, ventilation systems, and hidden laboratories in the Alien Encounters Expansion Pack.

Featuring: 
New environment: Hangar 68
Hiway Hauler™ 2;
Test Subject™;
Speed Slayer™;
Swamp Buggy.

📘 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HotWheelsUnleashed/
